Want to restore the planet’s ecosystems and see your impact in monthly videos? The first 100 people to join Planet Wild with my code PRACTICAL10 will get the first month for free at: https://planetwild.com/r/practicalengineering/join
If you want to get to know them better first, check out their project protecting the Little Owl https://planetwild.com/r/practicalengineering/m4

An ode to the engineering of guyed masts: Cool to look at, incredibly tall, just rare enough that seeing one is kind of special.

Watch this video ad-free on Nebula: https://nebula.tv/videos/practical-engineering-the-bizarre-bases-of-antenna-towers

Signed copies of my book (plus other cool stuff) are available here: https://store.practical.engineering/
